<div class="toolpinglun"><a href="/xiefanyi.aspx?shiID=22"><img src="/img/write.png" / alt="" width="18" height="18"/></a></div>
<div class="toolpinglun" style=" margin-top:-4px;"><a href="/randShowNew.aspx?id=4326"><img src="/img/bootmright.png" alt="下一首" width="26" height="26" /></a></div>
